1292
00:42:54,993 --> 00:42:56,593
- Bagi kami... - Beberapa ribu.

1293
00:42:56,593 --> 00:42:58,363
- Ya ampun. - Sekitar 4.000 orang melamar...

1294
00:42:58,363 --> 00:42:59,893
